					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You guys are completely confusing CHRRAM with SRAM, wich are two completely different things. SOROM allows SRAM to be bankswitched, while CPROM allows CHRRAM to be bankswitched. No mapper will ever allow CHRRAM to be written to outside of VBlank, until you have a dual port SRAM. This will most likely never be possible with the power pack either.</div>

